{"word":"κείω 1","slug":"κείω 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n56409\" key=\"kei/w1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κείω</orth> (A), once in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κέω</orth> (v. infr., cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0082.tlg002:143:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.D.\">A.D.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">143.11</biblScope> </bibl>), <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> Desiderat. of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κεῖμαι, βῆ δ᾽ ἴμεναι κείων</foreign> he went <sense id=\"n56409.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to lie down</tr_>, went <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to bed</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:532\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.532</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:18:428\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.428</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔνθ᾽ ἴομεν κείοντες</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:340\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.340</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κείω</foreign> I <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">will lie</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:19:340\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.340</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κειέμεν οὕτω</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">that they will lie</tr_> thus, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:8:315\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.315</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄρσο κέων</foreign> get thee <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to bed</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:7:342\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.342</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n56409.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> later, simply, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sleep, rest</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0653.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1009\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arat.\">Arat.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1009</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}